es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d45481a8b1211bb5eed12bb86a7c3a0287c43a","tid":366990,"uid":13768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前係銅鑼灣返工放lunch成日去食，<br />\n開頭都覺得幾正，雞扒夠大塊<br />\n最正係蔥油同咸酸菜<br />\n但後期唔知做乜，d飯勁淋，明顯落太多水果隻<br />\nd雞扒開始煎到又乾又勁油。<br />\n<br />\n最後轉去隔離果間食豬扒飯，又大塊又厚又香又多飯，都係貴幾蚊</blockquote><br />\n隔離豬扒飯好食一百倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n榮式真係狗也不屌，好撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58f374622feda96539030dc424ae53e80b4bed6","tid":366990,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我鍾意食佢個蓮藕餅 , 其他真係不了</blockquote><br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 , 個個都叫雞扒 , 我就覺得除左蓮藕餅其他都好難食</blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n藕餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n菜甫都好</blockquote><br />\n識食呀 , 次次都送飯 , 多多都食得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢啲菜莆得幾條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以問佢攞<br />\n雞扒係油左啲，但都叫皮脆肉嫩啦<br />\n平時講茶記連登仔就話狗也不屌<br />\n但講親有名氣既店就話是但一間茶記屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登仔係咁戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c0835ae8b85522db7f24775a9765e70c603aab","tid":366990,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:07:35.000Z","msg":"灣仔食肆只要唔係屎都排長龍，戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"7d37603d98a7c8914d8e0fc53feef2e897ef92d5","tid":366990,"uid":37131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"一開頭真係好食，但越做越麻麻地仲要好貴"},{"pid":"2f20776e6093c3f5001769e6be84a9e6ad874e16","tid":366990,"uid":129922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"好似間間唔同味道"},{"pid":"dc94bf6b93077824ee52dfce0ae4f64c90ebbab9","tid":366990,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無你地講到咁差呀，真係狗也不屌就執柒左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 見灣仔鋪lunch人滿為患</blockquote><br />\n灣仔如果連lunch都唔滿就晨早執柒左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以咪話未至於狗也不屌囉，你話一般貨色就真既。</blockquote><br />\n意思係灣仔呢啲地方，打工仔面對呢種價位既飯，合埋眼食飽就算，仲會諗咩好唔好味。當然你話一定要拎狗飯出來比，咁當打和啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d5264c32a2ed02775a37e2fae700bfe2ed8a78","tid":366990,"uid":100331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:17:39.000Z","msg":"屯市好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最愛撈檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6107ac8ee429e47795e565856bf4f345d219a11b","tid":366990,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"個名好柒，咩榮式 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0150e5611b59dc6972eeb2acf9d2e3d61d3e2295","tid":366990,"uid":109809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"幾好食<br />\n不過服務態度極差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e093089b91d399e41b80d84d1c4b7ae5cf287b39","tid":366990,"uid":64696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"究竟你地平時係食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講親咩都係難食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f883550f4c68ffe65f4be71aabaf8dc10ce1f18","tid":366990,"uid":92535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"香港仔個間食過一次 <br />\n難食到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49e35e9eb49198ad09b0e439ba2fe2af7ab03d5","tid":366990,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟你地平時係食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講親咩都係難食咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食開屎啊，sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1d320be3e15f73b592a423676531e97ffeebae","tid":366990,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:11:50.000Z","msg":"唔撚飽<br />\n你食埋我嗰份"},{"pid":"c0a6bb197d95d7a798f7d9e0c12ad4aee6047c6b","tid":366990,"uid":55937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:42:31.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人食過都話啲飯淋，即係我食果次唔係單一事件啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26789b6f7558b7a7800812cc3cdb3163bd70422d","tid":366990,"uid":76735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:45:18.000Z","msg":"好難食認真<br />\n啲雞扒乾到好似柴皮咁"},{"pid":"24630fc90ed196e015e3d6603a6e76b8c1384a07","tid":366990,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:51:24.000Z","msg":"一時時 好飄忽 可能總店好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483f71b81f1854a8ed7f68333dec5cd4ec1930ed","tid":366990,"uid":49815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:55:49.000Z","msg":"又乾又凍 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食過佐敦果間已經伏<br />\n以為第間好啲 試埋禮頓道果邊嗰間<br />\n