ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:09:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8a80c87f2cf4f5a53ae5d14b732655d085dce81","tid":366990,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T19:19:30.000Z","msg":"以前成日食屯門個間 連鎖黎講算唔錯"},{"pid":"00959dd5cac6e00f084402a8f12805dd488e7da7","tid":366990,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T21:06:41.000Z","msg":"好耐之前一開始灣仔第一間就幾好食既 塊皮燒得好脆<br />\n而家狗也不屌！！"},{"pid":"b1ef3e2a64d54955ef20a9f9b587bdae2a04ce76","tid":366990,"uid":21636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T21:23:42.000Z","msg":"之前第一次就食烏冬，屌你老母難撚食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328a9b5c0657bf15ecec7d3008d11cf40a35609d","tid":366990,"uid":108078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T21:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個飯一係太濕一大太乾 D油多到浸飯咁 都算 重點係試過幾次俾D員工朋友截糊 屌你老味 我LUNCH得個一個鍾鬆D 一埋位都急到仆街 你班MK隊都唔洗排都算 我叫雞扒飯 佢夠膽黎個淨飯叫我食住先 隔離枱2條友十塊雞扒即上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最尾嬲到走左去食茶記"},{"pid":"4b5bb6bbb7c1bd9176cb524e85088acafbcb3455","tid":366990,"uid":39948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T22:41:27.000Z","msg":"其實成日話同街市買既一樣係咪真係食過？佢將塊雞扒拍扁左，等佢入味啲同埋會去左個骨位<br />\n的確係冇以前咁好食，塊皮冇咁脆，不過講到同一般茶記一樣就唔係事實"},{"pid":"ed38abe57de52fc1fdd4ed89e8fdfd4e4eea5560","tid":366990,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T23:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實成日話同街市買既一樣係咪真係食過？佢將塊雞扒拍扁左，等佢入味啲同埋會去左個骨位<br />\n的確係冇以前咁好食，塊皮冇咁脆，不過講到同一般茶記一樣就唔係事實</blockquote><br />\n街市好多醃左九年既去骨雞扒一定好味過佢"},{"pid":"fbebefb2bd8692f44d3cfe3719ca062932c8538c","tid":366990,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:01:59.000Z","msg":"有冇好食既雞扒推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48f4a4a5585defcbe065fae3ecfa94658162c5b","tid":366990,"uid":58049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:16:04.000Z","msg":"肥撚到仆街"},{"pid":"66f01269454a44164ed65d929c293616896dbc44","tid":366990,"uid":55937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前成日食屯門個間 連鎖黎講算唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前喺灣仔返工 每個星期食一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家請我都唔撚食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a16d08031137d3cb03197a0cd59beb56e7d1df","tid":366990,"uid":33668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T01:24:01.000Z","msg":"好少可打手POST<br />\n<br />\n連個助攻都未進場就見到一面倒劣評<br />\n<br />\n開POST果個份工無喇無喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc10c1886c9833d8c32396e4e1f32c564fba99d","tid":366990,"uid":55937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好少可打手POST<br />\n<br />\n連個助攻都未進場就見到一面倒劣評<br />\n<br />\n開POST果個份工無喇無喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主問榮式有冇機會超越譚仔  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef175825fd61a794661971b58fcfdc0bfc0867df","tid":366990,"uid":49815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T07:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好少可打手POST<br />\n<br />\n連個助攻都未進場就見到一面倒劣評<br />\n<br />\n開POST果個份工無喇無喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />